         MACRO                                                          00160000
.*                                                                      00170000
.* Branch and Save on condition                                         00180000
.*                                                                      00190000
&LABEL   BASC  &COND,                  * Condition                     *00200000
               &REG,                   * Register for return address   *00210000
               &DEST,                  * Destination address or (reg)  *00220000
               &TYPE=LOCAL             * BAS/BASR                       00230000
